This PR adds the getSoundGroup() method in Block which returns a BlockSoundGroup

diff --git a/src/main/java/io/papermc/paper/block/BlockSoundGroup.java b/src/main/java/io/papermc/paper/block/BlockSoundGroup.java
new file mode 100644
